commit.message:
refactor FileStatus as class, add `--mathlib4` (#137)

To further support mathlib porting, the `FileStatus` tracker is refactored.
This will allow for better parsing long-term, easier node annotation (like href linking).

For QOL, one can pass a `mathlib4` path to color node outlines as red for existing files.
